OL,3,CMillions missing out on smart meter
OL,4,Cbenefits due to faults and poor service
OL,6,FMillions of households are missing out
OL,7,Fon the benefits of their smart meter
OL,8,Fdue to faults and poor service from
OL,9,Ftheir supplier, Citizens Advice has
OL,10,Fwarned.
OL,12,FMore than half of British homes now
OL,13,Fhave a smart meter, but the consumer
OL,14,Fadvice charity says they are being let
OL,15,Fdown by suppliers who are often
OL,16,F"nowhere to be found" when problems
OL,17,Farise.
