OL,6,FA survey for the charity found 20% of
OL,7,Fhouseholds with a smart meter ` 2.86
OL,8,Fmillion households ` still have to
OL,9,Fregularly submit manual meter readings
OL,10,Fbecause their device is not doing this
OL,11,Fautomatically.
OL,13,FAlmost a third (31%) experienced
OL,14,Fissues with their in-home display
OL,15,Fscreen that helps households track
OL,16,Ftheir energy usage and costs.
OL,18,FA quarter of people who asked Citizens
OL,19,FAdvice for help with smart meter
OL,20,Fissues had billing problems.
