OL,6,F"Energy companies are very keen for
OL,7,Fcustomers to get a smart meter but
OL,8,Fwhen issues arise they are often
OL,9,Fnowhere to be found. That has to
OL,10,Fchange. Suppliers have been far too
OL,11,Fsluggish in fixing issues with problem
OL,12,Fmeters.
OL,14,F"New obligations and stronger
OL,15,Faccountability measures are needed to
OL,16,Frestore public trust in this vital
OL,17,Ftool to reach net zero."
