OL,6,FIndependent non-profit Smart Energy GB
OL,7,Fsaid: "The vast majority of smart
OL,8,Fmeters are operating as they should
OL,9,Fand it's good to see this report
OL,10,Fhighlight that most smart meter owners
OL,11,Fare happy with them.
OL,13,F"However, if you're among the minority
OL,14,Fwith a smart meter that isn't
OL,15,Fcurrently sending readings
OL,16,Fautomatically to your supplier then we
OL,17,Funderstand this can be frustrating.
