OL,6,F"Please be assured that if your meter
OL,7,Fisn't currently sending readings
OL,8,Fautomatically, it should still be
OL,9,Frecording your energy use and your
OL,10,Fenergy won't cost you more.
OL,12,F"We would recommend that you contact
OL,13,Fyour supplier if you experience an
OL,14,Fissue with your smart meter and send
OL,15,Fthem regular meter readings to make
OL,16,Fsure you receive accurate, rather than
OL,17,Festimated, bills until all of the
OL,18,Ffeatures of your smart meter have been
OL,19,Frestored."
