OL,6,FThe Department for Energy Security and
OL,7,FNet Zero said: "Energy suppliers are
OL,8,Frequired to keep their customers'
OL,9,Fmeters working and Ofgem is
OL,10,Fresponsible for regulating them
OL,11,Fagainst this requirement.
OL,13,F"Any issues with smart meters and in
OL,14,Fhome display screens should be
OL,15,Faddressed promptly and we will soon
OL,16,Fannounce plans to drive better service
OL,17,Ffor new and existing smart meter
OL,18,Fcustomers."
