OL,6,FAn Ofgem spokesperson said: "While the
OL,7,Fmajority of smart meters are working
OL,8,Fcorrectly, we've asked suppliers to
OL,9,Fprovide us with more detail on how
OL,10,Fthey plan to tackle connectivity
OL,11,Fissues.
OL,13,F"Suppliers are responsible for making
OL,14,Fsure their customers' smart meters
OL,15,Foperate correctly, and we expect them
OL,16,Fto communicate with their customers
OL,17,Fclearly if there are any issues with
OL,18,Ftheir smart meter."
